- ‚úÖ **Use srcset for different image sizes**
- ‚úÖ **Use picture element for art direction**
- ‚úÖ **Implement lazy loading for below-fold images**
- ‚úÖ **Serve modern formats (WebP, AVIF) with fallbacks**

