## ‚ùå DON'T (Anti-patterns)

### Layout Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Desktop-first approach**: Don't design for desktop and scale down
- ‚ùå **Fixed pixel widths**: Don't use `width: 1200px;` for containers
- ‚ùå **Horizontal scroll**: Don't allow horizontal scrolling (except carousels)
- ‚ùå **Too many breakpoints**: Don't create breakpoints for every device

```css
/* ‚ùå Bad: Desktop-first with max-width */
.container {
  width: 1200px;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .container { width: 960px; }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .container { width: 100%; }
}

/* ‚úÖ Good: Mobile-first with min-width */
.container {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 1rem;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
}

@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .container {
    max-width: 960px;
  }
}
```

### Image Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Single large image**: Don't serve desktop images to mobile
- ‚ùå **Missing dimensions**: Don't omit width/height attributes (causes layout shift)
- ‚ùå **No lazy loading**: Don't load all images immediately
- ‚ùå **Unoptimized formats**: Don't use only JPEG/PNG

```html
<!-- ‚ùå Bad: Single image for all devices -->
<img src="huge-image-4k.jpg" alt="Product">

<!-- ‚ùå Bad: Missing dimensions causes layout shift -->
<img src="image.jpg" alt="Product">

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: Responsive with dimensions -->
<img 
  src="image-800w.jpg"
  srcset="image-400w.jpg 400w, image-800w.jpg 800w, image-1200w.jpg 1200w"
  sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 1024px) 80vw, 1200px"
  alt="Product"
  loading="lazy"
  width="800"
  height="600">
```

### Typography Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Fixed font sizes**: Don't use only pixels for font sizes
- ‚ùå **Tiny text**: Don't use font sizes below 16px on mobile (causes zoom)
- ‚ùå **Poor readability**: Don't create long lines on wide screens
- ‚ùå **No scaling**: Don't prevent text zoom with `maximum-scale=1`

```html
<!-- ‚ùå Bad: Prevents user zoom (accessibility issue) -->
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: Allows zoom -->
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
```

```css
/* ‚ùå Bad: Fixed typography doesn't scale */
body { font-size: 14px; }
h1 { font-size: 32px; }

/* ‚úÖ Good: Scalable typography */
body { font-size: clamp(1rem, 0.9rem + 0.5vw, 1.125rem); }
h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 1.5rem + 2.5vw, 4rem); }
```

### Touch Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Small tap targets**: Don't make buttons smaller than 44√ó44px
- ‚ùå **Hover-only interactions**: Don't rely on hover states on mobile
- ‚ùå **No touch feedback**: Don't ignore active/pressed states
- ‚ùå **Dense spacing**: Don't pack interactive elements too closely

```css
/* ‚ùå Bad: Too small for touch */
.button {
  padding: 4px 8px;
  font-size: 12px;
}

/* ‚ùå Bad: Hover-only dropdown (doesn't work on touch) */
.dropdown:hover .menu {
  display: block;
}

/* ‚úÖ Good: Click/tap to open */
.dropdown[aria-expanded="true"] .menu {
  display: block;
}
```

### Content Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Hiding critical features**: Don't hide important features on mobile
- ‚ùå **Different content**: Don't show different content on mobile vs desktop
- ‚ùå **Separate mobile site**: Don't create m.example.com (use responsive design)
- ‚ùå **Reordering in HTML**: Don't change HTML order for different devices

